{"tid":2041180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"396人被拘分送五署 80青少年先准保釋  家長通宵撐子女 轟警濫捕","createTime":"2020-05-29T05:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T08:11:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f20e918272b3d77771e2e47daff725b51a8ba193","tid":2041180,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T05:25:34.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200529/CTNXLKLL43YNPD24Z4O7KBJ4WA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200529%2FCTNXLKLL43YNPD24Z4O7KBJ4WA%2F&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33AZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=60493614\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200529%2FCTNXLKLL43YNPD24Z4O7KBJ4WA%2F&h=54e47f92\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200529/CTNXLKLL43YNPD24Z4O7KBJ4WA/</a><br />\n<br />\n396人被拘分送五署 80青少年先准保釋 <br />\n家長通宵撐子女 轟警濫捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【5.27圍捕】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版國安法獲全國人大表決通過前夕，港人反惡法抗爭到底，前日警方在全港軍管式佈防，無差別大圍捕近400人，當中80人未成年。昨凌晨時分，不少親友及家長帶同食物、拖鞋等在警署外通宵守候，但除未成年被捕人士凌晨起獲准保釋，至昨深夜仍有近200人未獲釋。有被拘留12小時後獲保釋的14歲學生聲言，只是經過銅鑼灣希慎廣場便被捕。昨早亦有家長到警署為子女送食物以示支持，其中葉太更斥警方濫捕：「行吓街唱吓歌仔，響呢一刻我哋仲係自由嘅，冇做任何嘢，點解要咁樣做？」<br />\n<br />\n記者：李家傑 劉漢權 鄭文輝<br />\n<br />\n警方前日在全港拘捕396人，被捕者由12至70歲，當中180人為學生、80人未成年。據知他們涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器、藏有工具。。。。。。。香港仔警署。昨凌晨起，80名未成年人士先後獲保釋，由通宵守候的家人接回家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5LFAPHOTEUSPA5ZPYWXMZAQB24.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5LFAPHOTEUSPA5ZPYWXMZAQB24.gif&h=575eab93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【北角警署】至昨晚11時，仍有大批家屬在北角警署外守候；議員許智峯到場協助，批評警方歎慢板。黎樹雄攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FCMAS3U52LSZ32MSO2FJOREJ4M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFCMAS3U52LSZ32MSO2FJOREJ4M.jpg&h=a5a4437a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【紅磡警署】昨日凌晨，多名家長在警署外徹夜等待保釋子女。鄭文輝攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KNYTWBLY5X3JWFE3TPVOKPTF3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKNYTWBLY5X3JWFE3TPVOKPTF3Y.jpg&h=8e822594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有家屬帶同水果及拖鞋等候被捕者獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警逼叫口號嘲弄14歲女生<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：一句「防暴警跑緊嚟」學生被搜屋<br />\n<br />\n前晚深夜開始，包括被捕者親友、區議員及義工等約200人在北角警署外守候，部份人甚至等通宵。其中，前日下午於銅鑼灣被捕的14歲女生，遭扣查12小時後終獲准保釋，她。。。。。。。。。。乜嘢口號都冇嗌！」她又指，在警署待證物拍照期間遭警員嘲弄，「叫我叫句『五大訴求 缺一不可』嚟聽吓。」前日在朗豪坊外遭警員以涉嫌非法集結拘捕的兩名女生，昨凌晨亦由家人保釋回家。<br />\n<br />\n葉太仍在求學的21歲兒子，同樣在希慎廣場外被捕，昨晨她趁上班前買早餐到北角警署送交兒子，「話畀佢聽屋企人喺門口支持佢，叫佢唔使驚，攞個麵包畀佢，起碼佢。。。。。。。。。。。是叫口號及唱歌，非在前線抗爭，防暴警員叫人群後退離開，卻前後拉起封鎖線包抄圍捕。對於兒子和平表達訴求卻遭拘押，她坦言心情矛盾：「想佢可以幫到香港，但邊個想有事吖！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MFY6RRKPOZLJ4S4JA3X4TWBNJY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMFY6RRKPOZLJ4S4JA3X4TWBNJY.gif&h=226e9f45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩名仍身穿校服的女生於紅磡警署分別由父母接走。鄭文輝攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A2RNGZKYGM5MIRQ6DWKOSGXEPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA2RNGZKYGM5MIRQ6DWKOSGXEPM.jpg&h=15b889a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n社工呂智恆昨凌晨帶同標語到北角聲援被捕人士。 李家傑攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「企喺度乜都冇做」仍被捕<br />\n<br />\n紅磡警署外亦有數十人通宵守候，放滿大量食物飲品。有獲釋的16歲男生稱，當時完成網上課堂前往用膳，途中被警員截停，未問其目的便以涉嫌參與非法集結拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n社工呂智恆凌晨亦在北角警署外高舉標語聲援被捕人士，他。。。。。。。。。。。「只係企喺度乜都冇做過」卻在銅鑼灣被捕，其中有友人剛當上爸爸，對警方一再濫捕感不滿。"},{"pid":"e6596ae164c8a0ece5ffc147c98d3f435c8bd632","tid":2041180,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T01:56:35.000Z","msg":"兩個女生 - 陳惜姿<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2042897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2042897</a>"},{"pid":"8a21d33c597bd0efe410b1845e87b01e202d74c2","tid":2041180,"uid":51200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T02:36:05.000Z","msg":"CLS<br />\n個frd 中環OL裝<br />\n行過拉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45af33e1c94c13ab21f496b7c98383ed72c5f8b0","tid":2041180,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T02:37:50.000Z","msg":"呂智恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新民主同盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃良喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /